                     <interp inst="t17530906-52-off275" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing two gold rings set with stones, value eleven shillings, one pair of sleeve buttons, value one shilling, one silver Four-pence, and one silver Three-pence
            </rs>, the goods and monies of 
               <persName id="t17530906-52-victim500" type="victimName">
                  Eleanor 
                  Collier 
               <interp inst="t17530906-52-victim500" type="surname" value="Collier"></interp>
