                     <interp inst="t17530906-52-person505" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner at the bar these ten years, and never heard any bad character of him in all my whole life.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17530906-52-person506">
                  Martha 
                  Lee 
               <interp inst="t17530906-52-person506" type="surname" value="Lee"></interp>
