                     <interp inst="t17530906-52-person506" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner these twenty years, and never heard he wrong'd any body in my life.</p>
               <p>Q. Have you seen him in common within these two years?</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17530906-52-person507">
                  Martha 
                  Lee 
